62.6	Maitreya	Maitreya	Maitreya , Metteyya (Pāli), or Jampa (Tibetan), is foretold as a future Buddha of this world in Buddhist eschatology. In some Buddhist literature, such as the Amitabha Sutra and the Lotus Sutra, he or she is referred to as Ajita Bodhisattva.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/59/KushanMaitreya.JPG/220px-KushanMaitreya.JPG
